title: Worst Date Wednesday: She Drank the Cherry Jar Juice
description: Kyle tells us about the time he went out with a girl that was quite the trainwreck.  The beginning of the date went well until he got the bill and saw that there were extra shots and drinks on it that they didn't get.  He found out she was chugging drinks while he was in the bathroom.  And it keeps getting worse, including where she peed at one point...
